title: Focus on the Car Crash
itunes:title: Focus on the Car Crash
description:
Episode 621 - Whatever you focus on, you will get. So, 00what are you thinking about most of the time? Are you thinking about how you don't have money and then you wonder why you still don't have money? It's because you are focusing on not having money vs the solutions to add more dollars in your bank account. In this episode, I will dive deep into this topic and teach you how to focus on what it is that you want so that you can get it! Follow me on Instagram at https://www.instagram.com/robdialjr/
